dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, soundings, and spot heights. At head of title: Azores. Includes 3 cross sections and 3 insets: Caldeira das sete cidades, [scale ca. 1:32,000] -- Ponta Delgada, [scale ca. 1:10,000]-- Villa Franca road, [scale ca. 1:20,000]. North oriented to the upper left. "1854." "Published according to Act of Parliament ... July 23rd 1849." Historic Maps copy has label on verso: No. 1854.
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published ... at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the Admiralty charts, 21 Poultry, 1849.
